# Data Structure
 
RETORNOS

## success_200 (object)
+ code: 200 (number) - 200
+ mensagem: Success (string) - Success

## fail_400 (object)
+ code: 400 (number) - 400
+ mensagem: Bad request (string) - Bad request

## fail_401 (object)
+ code: 401 (number) - 401
+ mensagem: Unauthorized (string) - Unauthorized

## fail_404 (object)
+ code: 404 (number) - 404
+ mensagem: Not Found (string) - Not Found
